🧠 Project Overview

In this project, we implemented Infrastructure as Code (IaC) using Terraform to automate the creation of an AWS EBS snapshot from an existing volume.

This simulates a real-world DevOps use case where organizations need automated backups and disaster recovery mechanisms for critical storage systems.

Instead of manually creating snapshots via AWS Console, we defined the entire process using Terraform for repeatability, consistency, and scalability.

🎯 Objectives
Create an EBS volume using Terraform
Generate a snapshot from the volume
Ensure proper tagging and documentation of resources
Validate snapshot completion in AWS
